%p
  %b Hi #{@resource.first_name}!

%p Your account has been locked due to an excessive number of unsuccessful sign in attempts.

%p Click the link below to unlock your account:

%table{ border: "0", cellpadding: "0", cellspacing: "0", width: "100%" }
  %tr
    %td{ align: "center" }
      = link_to 'Unlock account', unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token), class: 'button'

%p Alternatively, you may also copy/paste the following link into your browser:
%b
  %em= unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token)

%p Thank you!

%p
  %b= Settings.application.name
